parameters:
Are you going back already? Since we haven't found
anything yet, let's keep trying a little longer!
I hope we can find some clues...
Wait-! Our date has only just begun!
Let's explore together a little while longer!

When you return to the village, it will be night
and today's exploration will come to an end.
Please take care.
Shall we return to the village...?
Should we go back to the village...

Huh... There were various things I wanted to come
back to.
Let's go check it out right away.

Beyond the magic circle, another magic circle was
waiting.
The sun will set soon even here today.
It's a little disappointing, but let's try again.

They returned to the town with a new magic circle
appearing behind them...
Are you ready in your heart?
Are you ready in your heart?
あ、いえ、まだちょっと・・・
A voice can be heard from up ahead.

I wonder who it is? It's not someone from the
village...

Hey, brother. Shouldn't we be moving on to the
next step soon?

The next step? I am satisfied with my current
life, but...

Absolutely shameless, but still proud, the second
son of the honorable Oku3 brothers, huh? Okutayo,
you should say it too.

I'm satisfied as long as everyone can live without
hunger, but...
That's right... It's important not to go hungry.

But we should aim higher! Let's become the world's
greatest monsters!
Oh no, it's a monster! What should we do, \n[1]...

He insisted that we need to find a clue as soon as
possible.

...That's right, whether it's a monster or
whatever it is, we have to defeat it and move
forward!

That's right, we definitely can't win if we fight
in our current state.
For today, let's just go back to the village.

If those monsters are there, it seems like we
won't be able to proceed any further.

I silently agreed with that opinion and left the
place.
You must be evil demons for sure!

For the sake of Light and the people of the
village who are suffering...
I'll punish you here and now!

She jumps out in front of the monsters, readying
her weapon.
It's rare for humans to come this far...

It seems like they're scary people. We should
quietly run away from here.

Calm down! If you look closely, they're just
children, aren't they?
There's no way you can beat us!

I've come up with a great idea. Let's capture them
and use them as a stepping stone for our
ambitions!

I'm not particularly keen on dealing with
children, but...

No... that's true, but we still need to take
action. I think this is a chance!

Hey! Let's quickly run away from here and go back
home!

These monsters seem a bit noisier than the stories
we heard. It might be a little different.

But now's our chance! Let's do our best to defeat
them for Light's sake too!

I see, I may have underestimated them a bit
because they're children.
Uwaa! I told you we should stop, didn't I?!
Damn it! You're quite good, aren't you!

Thanks to the opponent's confusion, we managed to
successfully break through somehow.

However, if the opponent had come at us in perfect
condition, the result would have been different.

It was wrong to do something like this! Let's
quickly apologize and run away!

I'm sorry for the rough behavior. Okuni didn't
mean any harm.

If there's another opportunity, I'd like to have a
calm conversation at that time.
Um, I'm also sorry about this?
Don't worry about it, then farewell!

I was worried about how things would turn out, but
somehow it all worked out. Thank goodness.

I've never seen a monster before, and it was
different from what I had imagined.

The last monster I talked to might actually be a
good monster.

If we can talk, it might be useful for the future
exploration.

That's right! If we meet again, shall we talk a
little more?
\n[1] was so strong, it was kind of cool...

Ah, it's not like I'm usually incompetent or
anything! I mean, let me rephrase that!
When you say that, I feel a little embarrassed.

For now, let's head back today. \n[1] had a tough
time too, so it's better to rest.
He nodded and headed straight back to the village.

Pain ran through his whole body and his
consciousness began to fade.

Isn't that a bit too much? You should be a little
more considerate...

Shut up... Listen! I'll show you what a monster
is!
Hey, stop it and let go!

In the sinking consciousness, only Lira's voice
echoed.

It's finally time, huh \n[1]? I'm a little scared,
but let's do our best.

From here on, monsters will also appear, so let's
be careful.
I hope we find some clues.
Phew, somehow we managed to pull through...

Let's not push ourselves too hard and do our best
at this pace!
There is one crystal placed in each map.

You can recover here, so please make use of it for
dungeon conquest.

The path is blocked by something like a magic
circle.

This looks like the place you mentioned earlier...
What should we do?
Let's try to find some clues to pass through here.

It's shining... There's no mistake, it's
definitely a clue.
Hmm... It seems like I can reach it soon.
Margaret has fallen under the hole!

I tried to peek below, but it's too dark to see
clearly.

I lean forward a little more to see if I can't see
a bit better... Ah.

The path is blocked by something like a magic
circle.
Margaret... Why can't we proceed from here?
Let's try to find a clue to pass through here.

I'll let you know that I'll protect you no matter
what happens, so it's okay.

events.name: ブロ3日目妖精さんはじめ

parameters:
Geez, you're always the same. You should just
accept my love already!

You're troubled, right? I'll definitely be of
help.

Take me with you... okay? I'm worried about Light
too.
If that's the case, I reluctantly agree.

Come to think of it, we first met in a forest like
this, didn't we...

events.name: プロ3日目中盤イベント

parameters: Are you feeling unwell, big-breasted lady?
I think there were some good herbs over there.
Since we've come all this way, let's take it!

Since we're here, should we take it? I'm sure
it'll make the busty girl feel better!
Are you ready in your heart?
あ、いえ、まだちょっと・・・

There it is, there it is! It's the one growing
back there!
Kyaa! W-What is this thing coming over here?!

I have to help her, she's being
attacked by a monster!
I cut the vine entwining Miiru and set her free.
Haa... haa... I managed to pull through.
Ugh... my body feels all sticky for some reason...

I honestly thought I was done for, but \n[1]
quickly came to help me and I'm glad...
Don't worry about it, I'll wipe your body for you.
Sensing the danger, I quickly took her hand.
I-I'm sorry! It seems like I fainted for a bit.

I feel like something good happened, but I wonder
what it was...

Ah... yes, it's a medicinal herb! I remember it
clearly.
Um, the one right in front of me is that.

It's a very effective medicinal herb, so I'm sure
Onee-san's breasts will get better soon!
Look! A really beautiful gem has fallen!

It closely resembled the gem that Margaret found,
so it might be a clue to proceed further.

I have some reservations, but I will express my
gratitude sincerely.

Um... how many children do you want? I want to
live in a house where I can see a big World Tree!

Eh! To think about making a village with our
children...
Stop it! Hey... where did you...!

In the sinking consciousness, only Miiru's voice
calling for help could be heard...

It hurts a little, but there doesn't seem to be
any problem with the body.
Ask what happened to the monster after that.

Eh... the monster? U-um, it seems to have gone
somewhere

I was teased a little, but there doesn't seem to
be any pain.

I'm sure it was because we suddenly approached and
surprised it.
I'm relieved that it turned out that way

Ah... come to think of it, I managed to gather the
medicinal herbs, and look, I found a beautiful gem
too.

It closely resembled the gem Margaret found, so it
might be a clue to proceed further.
I'm glad... I could be of help

Light is worried that Miiru is looking a little
down and wonders if something is wrong.

More importantly, look! Since I found this gem
with such effort,
Let's try going a little further ahead!
With this, it looks like we can move forward.

Good job! It felt wonderful working together with
the two of you!

It looks dangerous to explore further, so let's
head back for today!

Well, if \n[1] says he won't go home today, I don't
mind staying here...

It looks dangerous to explore further, so let's
head back for today.
It looks like we can move forward with this.

Good job! It feels like we're in the clear with
the results!

I'm feeling tired today, so let's head home for
now, okay?

Well, if \n[1] says he's not going home today, then
I don't mind staying here...

It's dangerous to stay any longer, so let's go
home.

events.name: 選択イベント初期化イベ

parameters: Oh, it seems like you're having fun, Lira.

Ah, sorry! I know it's not the right situation for
that, but...

I just thought it would be nice to do something
together with the three of us like this.

I feel like I understand what Lira is saying. We
do see each other every day, but it's not like
we're doing anything special together.

Even if there were some tasks to do, it feels like
it's for the whole village, so doing something
with the three of us together like this is really
rare.

Somehow, I feel like I understand a little and I'm
getting excited too.

Yeah! If the three of us cooperate like we used
to, dispelling curses will be a piece of cake!

Margaret, are you okay? Be careful because the
ground is slippery.
...Is Light okay in terms of health and curses?

I'm sorry for worrying you. Thanks to your
concern, my health has improved quite a bit.

I'm just a little worried about the curses,
though.

I reminded him not to overdo it and told him to
follow up immediately if anything happens.

I don't really think it's a good idea for Light to
explore.

But I know that both \n[1] and Light are stubborn
once they've decided to do something.
Thank you for including me too

Well, it feels a bit wasteful, but it's because
it's Light, huh--

I think if it were someone I didn't know, they
would be really angry, right?

Lira and Margaret, as well as everyone, are all
special!

Because he was very kind to me, well! But the
number one is \n[1]!
Haha, as usual, \n[1] is quite popular, isn't he?

He lets out a sigh, saying that he's honestly
troubled.

\n[1] can hear you, you know! He's always so
distant as usual...

Be careful, as monsters will start appearing from
here.

...Was it okay for \n[1] and me to go alone?
Everyone seemed like they wanted to go together.

I feel bad for Light, but I honestly didn't want
to put everyone else in danger.

So, does that mean it's okay for me to go
separately? ...Yeah, I'll be fine.
Well, it's actually just \n[1] and me, though.

Light smiled meaningfully, which was a little
creepy, so I lightly nudged his shoulder.
Haha, sorry! ...Well then, shall we go, \n[1]?

events.name: 初回ダンジョンスイッチ

parameters: Move to the Northern Forest Riverside?
Do you want to move there?
Move to the Northern Forest Riverside?
Move to the North Forest Riverside?

You can't proceed beyond this point, as a barrier
has been set up ahead of Ral-La Village.
If you still insist on going, I won't stop you.

Are you with the young lady from the item shop? I
quite like her, but for now, should I prioritize
the treasure?
It's a dead end... I'll go check it out for now.
Do you want to move there?
Do you want to move there?
Would you like to move to the Laruura Ruins?
